","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was climbing Mount Uhud with Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman when it began to quake because of them. The Prophet said, \u201cBe still, Uhud! It is but a Prophet, a truthful man, and two martyrs upon you!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/04\/04\/four-khulafa-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":43710,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet foretells Four Righteous Caliphs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Safinah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Caliphate after me will last for thirty years, then there will be kingship.\u201d Sa\u2019id said to Safinah, \u201cCount the Caliphates of Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman?\u201d Then, Safinah said, \u201cYou must count the Caliphate of Ali.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":43710,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with h